Feature: Paymaart - Admin Web- Specific Merchant KYC verification View
    As a Super admin/admin, I want the ability to view a Specific KYC request of customers, agents, and merchants awaiting manual KYC verification.
    Conditions of Satisfaction
    There should be an option to view all the basic details and KYC details filled in by the customer, merchants, and agents

    Information to be displayed
    Merchant KYC details

    KYC type
    1.Full KYC
    2.Simplified KYC

    KYC status
    1a."Not started" if KYC verification is not started.
    1b. "Inprogress" if the KYC verification is in progress.
    1c. "Completed" if the KYC verification is completed and Succesfull.
    1d. “Further information required” if the KYC verification have been reviewed and rejected.

